## GroupList

### List with SVG and Base64 icon

```js
import Button from '../Button';

const listItems = [
  {
    title: 'Example title',
    subtitleElement: <div>subtitle</div>,
    icon: 'wallet',
    extra: <Button text='Go up'/>,
    id: '1',
  },
  {
    title: 'Other example title',
    subtitleElement: <div>subtitle</div>,
    imageUrl:
      'data:image/svg+xml;base64,',
    extra: <Button text='Go down'/>,
    id: '2',
  },
];
<GroupList items={listItems}/>
```
